name: Hamilton U.S. Equity YIELD MAXIMIZER TM ETF
longDescription: SMAX is designed for attractive monthly income, while providing exposure to a portfolio of primarily large-cap U.S. equity securities. To supplement dividend income earned on the equity holdings, mitigate risk and reduce volatility, SMAX will employ a covered call option writing program. SMAX does not use leverage. The investment objective of SMAX is to deliver attractive monthly income, while providing exposure to a portfolio of primarily largecap U.S. equity securities.
